properties.areaDesc: Otero Mesa; Northern Hudspeth Highlands/Hueco Mountains
properties.senderName: NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 20 at 3:06AM MST until February 20 at 6:00PM MST by NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...East to northeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50
mph expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Far Eastern El Paso, Western Hudspeth, and
Southern Otero Counties, including the Otero Mesa, and areas
west of the Hueco Mountains.

* WHEN...Until 6 PM MST this evening.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...A strong backdoor cold front will bring
strong easterly winds to the region beginning this morning. Wind
gusts may reach 50 mph in a few places, especially west of area
mountains.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM MST THIS EVENING
